headline: Best-Selling Cessna Citation Latitude Achieves FAA Certification for New, Advanced Features for Garmin G5000 Avionics
summary: WICHITA, Kan., September 24, 2025--The best-selling Cessna Citation Latitude, designed and produced by Textron Aviation Inc., a Textron Inc. (NYSE: TXT) company, has achieved Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) certification for new features of the Garmin G5000 avionics suite. These features include Synthetic Vision Guidance System (SVGS) for improved approach capabilities down to 150 feet, GDL 60 Datalink for connectivity and a new taxiway routing feature.
